### EduPortal API - Files Controller
### File upload and management endpoints (Not fully implemented)
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/files
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### UPLOAD FILE
### Note: Use multipart/form-data for actual file upload
### ===========================================
# POST {{baseUrl}}/upload?category=documents
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
#
# [file content]

### ===========================================
### DOWNLOAD FILE
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/download/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### DELETE FILE
### ===========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
